        {
            "title": "鴻海3月、首季營收創同期高 AI機櫃續出貨續強Q2估雙增",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/niS7MEDxjRNV8evQ8CJA1g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/5f690df59346faf5337d120f0c8f024e\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%B4%BB%E6%B5%B73%E6%9C%88-%E9%A6%96%E5%AD%A3%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E5%89%B5%E5%90%8C%E6%9C%9F%E9%AB%98-ai%E6%A9%9F%E6%AB%83%E7%BA%8C%E5%87%BA%E8%B2%A8%E7%BA%8C%E5%BC%B7q2%E4%BC%B0%E9%9B%99%E5%A2%9E-081349272.html",
